To use the atMega16, the USBasp and USB TTL Driver the following could be installed in order to connect and upload the code to the MEGATron Board v1.0
Please note the softwares required are present in the same repository with branch named: Softwares
1. AVRStudio 4.0 - This is an IDE which can be used to build and upload the hex file to the board.
2. AVRBurner to the system - Used to upload the data from AVRStudio 4.0 to the MEGATron board using the USBAsp Programmer ![alt text](https://github.com/ronnitp/i3indyatechnology/blob/master/USBasp%20tomegatraon.jpg)
3. Go to the Drivers sub repository and download and install the drivers
